---
title: Sesame Crusted Pork Schnitzel with Charred Corn Brown Rice & Asian Slaw
description: Things are getting a fun tonight. We’re crumbing out succulent pork schnitzels in sesame seeds. Drizzle it in a garlic aioli for a hit
of rich flavour and serve on top of charred corn brown rice for that classic schnitzel meal feel.
